translation[8]{c,v,t}:
  6,111,"Kananjalo ukuba Sasinokuthumela iingelosi kubo, baza nabafileyo bathetha nabo, Saza Thina Sahlanganisa zonke izinto phambi kwamehlo abo, babengayi kukholwa Engathandanga uAllâh. Kodwa uninzi lwabo luziphatha ngobudenge"
  6,112,"Ke ngoko Sinyulele uMprofeti ngamnye iintshaba ooSathana phakathi koluntu neejinni, bephefumlelana ngeentetho ezihonjisiweyo eziluwexulo (oluyinkohliso), ukuba iNkosi yakho Ibithande ngolo hlobo bebengazi kuyenza loo nto; bayeke ke nemiqambo yabo yamampunge"
  6,113,"(Oku kwenziwe) khon’ukuze iintliziyo zabo bangakholwayo kuBomi oBuzayo zinamathele kuloo nkohliso, kwanokuba bahlale (benjalo) bekholisekile yiyo, kwanokuba benze ezo zinto bazenzayo (zonke iintlobo zezono)"
  6,114,"(Yithi Muhammad) Ndifune mgwebi wumbi na endaweni ka-Allâh, lo gama inguYe Onithumelele iNcwadi (i’Kur’ân), echaza, inike ingcombolo (yezinto). Abo Sibanike isiBhalo bayazi okokuba ityhilwe yiNkosi yakho ngenyaniso. Ke ungabi ngomnye wabo bathandabuzayo"
  6,115,"Kananjalo ilizwi leNkosi yakho lizalisekile ngenyaniso nangobulungisa. Akukho mntu unokuwatshintsha amazwi aKhe. Yaye Yena nguSokuva, uSolwazi"
  6,116,"Ke kaloku ukuba ungathobela uninzi lwabo basemhlabeni baya kukulahlekisa ube kude le eNdleleni ka-Allâh. Bona akukho nto bayilandelayo ngaphandle koqash-qash, yaye akukho nto yimbi abayenzayo ngaphandle kokuxoka"
  6,117,"Inene iNkosi yakho! Yiyo eyaziyo ukuba ngubani na olahlekileyo eNdleleni yaYo, kananjalo Imazi kakuhle okwisiKhokelo (sokwenene)"
  6,118,"Ke ngoko yityani (kuphela) loo nyama ekubizwe igama lika-Allâh (phezu kwayo xa ixhelwa), ukuba ngaba phofu niyakholwa kwiiVesi (zika-Allâh)"